extendedInfo.description: !FREE GAME - SPACE DOG - FREE GAME!The most popular Facebook game, finally on your Android! Space DogSpace Dog. Ever heard of him? What about the game? After having being played by more than 7 millions of Facebook users, he finally lands on your Android!The goal is fairly simple but yet cool and fun! Drag and launch Space Dog in the air to make him fly in the sky as far as possible while making him bounces on all the chicken paving the ground.There is no better way to relax after a hard day of work!You can also customize Space Dog with various items to increase his performances. The rocket or the hanglider will make him fly longer and further, while the super chicken will increase the efficiency of your bounces. There are up to 5 items to use in order to reach the first place of the world ranking!Compare your score with your friends on Twitter or the social platform OpenFeint! Will you manage to complete the 30 additional challenges that Space Dog offers you?***FUNCTIONALITIES***- Free!!!- A stress relieving game with a simple yet addictive gameplay!- 5 different items to use and combine- Social platform OpenFeint- 30 special challenges and world ranking!- Twitter integration:compare your score with friends in real time !A question or a bug?
